// Title: Logged on Users Enumeration
// Description: Detects attempts to list AD group memberships via log events.
// Data Source: SecurityEvent
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0007 - Discovery
//   Technique: T1069 - Permission Groups Discovery
// Severity: High

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4732 or EventID == 4735
| project TimeGenerated, Account, Computer, Activity
| order by TimeGenerated desc